          <li>Repairs and Maintenance</li>
          <li>Marketing and Advertising</li>
          <li>Security Costs</li>
          <li>Administrative and Office Expenses</li>
          <li>Other miscellaneous items</li>
        </ul>
      </li>
    </ul>

